# Digimon Directory

Hatched Digimon companions are stored here.

Each Digimon has their own directory:
```
digimon/
└── {DigimonName}/
    ├── digimon.md         # Main profile and stats
    ├── agent.md           # Agent configuration
    └── memories/
        ├── active.md      # Current memory buffer (150-300 lines)
        └── archive/       # Summarized old memories
```

Digimon are created by hatching Digitama.
Use `/hatch-digitama {name}` to create your first Digimon!
